MyDistOrd 0.0.1.1
----------------------------------------------------------------

* Speed improvement: removed calculation for columns, using a copy of the calculation
for rows instead.
* added option for multi-threaded processing via amap package. On the example matrix, 
parallel processing is actually slower compared to single-threaded. Option disabled by default.


MyDistOrd 0.0.1.1
----------------------------------------------------------------

* Changed readme and helpfile to indicate that *summer* is just one 
of many packages to create a additive relationship matrix


MyDistOrd 0.0.1.0
----------------------------------------------------------------

* Initial version
